Example to create an instance using the builder pattern 

     FacetRange facetRange = FacetRange.builder()
             .from(0.3)
             .fromStr("{fromStr}")
             .to(0.3)
             .toStr("{toStr}")
             .count(0.3)
             .total(0.3)
             .min(0.3)
             .max(0.3)
             .mean(0.3)
             .build()
